{
  "stem": "2539.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I understand that 1.5-- roughly 1.5 million people were killed in small places, in bigger places, in-- in villages.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "People were shot just like dead, either in their homes or put on-- on horse and buggy, or a-- a truck, taken out-- or they walked to their deaths.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A lot walked to their deaths.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were shot and put into the graves.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were nearly 1.5 million people in this eastern Poland and Ukraine that never made it to any camp-- never made it to any camp.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They killed them right there and then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They didn't bother having trains.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They didn't bother running the trains to any concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They didn't bother getting the gas.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They just shot them like-- like lambs!",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I get very angry when I hear-- when I don't hear the destruction of the ghettos mentioned on the same level as the camps.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It really hurts me, because I myself know thousands of people who were killed that way in eastern Poland and Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I can't understand why the emphasis is only on the camps.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, millions perished in the camps, but what about the 1.5 to 2 million that perished in the ghettos that never made it to the camps?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why aren't they being honored on the same level as the people in the camps?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because nobody saw them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Americans didn't arrive there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Russians came later when they were all killed!",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They couldn't liberate anybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Is this the reason that there it's not never mentioned-- that the ghettos-- the destruction of the ghettos is never mentioned?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because nobody saw them being killed?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because there were no survivors to tell on the spot when the Russians entered?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Russians were not interested, because they were fighting for their own lives.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
